text: Novomikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Mikhaylovsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 176 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Mesyagutovo, 8 km from Mikhaylovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Novomikhaylovka, Duvansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
